snippet.title: Jaded | First Look Trailer
snippet.description:
Jaded, a 3d psychedelic bullet hell is dropping on steam soon! Get the first look at what to expect from this early access launch! 

Development started just over a year ago, and now we have honed systems and mechanics and a very fun experience.

Keep an eye out for a stream coming soon!
